snippet.title: Chess Rush - Season 7 - Trailer
snippet.description:
Dear Grandmasters, Gabrielle will open Season 7 in a few hours. Introducing the new class of "Warlord", this Angel can switch between two forms: ranged and melee. Are you ready for her arrival?

New to Chess Rush? Chess Rush is the most exciting and innovative autobattler game for mobile! Exclusive game modes, unparalleled graphics, constant updates, a thriving community of players from all over the world... and completely free! Give it a try and find out what the fuss is all about!

Download Chess Rush now! ►► https://bit.ly/2kvFcF7
